Package ms.safi.btsync.dto

Domain classes used to produce and consume the JSON for BitTorrent Sync RESTful services.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BTSyncPreferences
    JavaBean implementation of BitTorrent Sync preferences.
    BTSyncResponse
    JavaBean implementation of a generic response from BitTorrent Sync.
    File
    JavaBean implementation of a file's information from BitTorrent Sync.
    Folder
    JavaBean implementation of a folder's information from BitTorrent Sync.
    FolderPreferences
    JavaBean implementation of a folder's preferences from BitTorrent Sync.
    Hosts
    JavaBean implementation of a list of Hosts.
    Peer
    JavaBean implementation of a folder peer's information.
    Secrets
    JavaBean implementation of a set of secrets.
    Speed
    JavaBean implementation of BitTorrent Sync's current upload and download speeds.
